thread.title: Nate Miller

author: Nate Miller
title: Nate Miller
text:
I have been an admin for multiple companies utilizing the Five9 Contact Center applications. I have used the applications in multiple facets of outbound/inbound contact centers, and can say that it is the best solution on the market. While it takes long to master all the suite has to offer, diving in and getting things created is simple.
If you are looking for an outbound dialer or looking to route inbound traffic, Five9 makes it a simple process from start to implementation.
